Class TestStorable

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
public class TestStorable
extends AbstractKVStorable

A simple concrete implementation of AbstractKVStorable to making tests. The data have two different attributes: first value and second value. The first one is a long and the second is an integer value.

Author:
Nils Thieme
